==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Strombus
<hw>Strom"bus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of marine gastropods in
which the shell has the outer lip dilated into a broad wing. It includes
many large and handsome species commonly called <altname>conch
shells</altname>, or <altname>conchs</altname>. See
<er>Conch</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stromeyerite</ent>⟦br⟧
